doc.after: In August 2009 Royal Mail unveiled a series of 30 stamps reflecting the 30th Olympiad about the coming Olympic and Paralympic Games They were released in batches of ten between 2009 and July 2011 each stamp featured an Olympic or Paralympic sport and the London 2012 logo 30 31 32
